g.text: IS THE ERROR TRANSIENT AND LIKELY TO BE RESOLVED AFTER A RETRY?
CONSIDER LINEAR RETRY STRATEGY FOR IMMEDIATE, CONSISTENT RETRIES.
IS THE ERROR POSSIBLY DUE TO A TEMPORARY SERVICE OVERLOAD OR INSTABILITY?
CONSIDER BACKOFF RETRY STRATEGY TO GIVE THE SERVICE MORE TIME TO RECOVER.
IS IT IMPORTANT TO PROGRESSIVELY INCREASE THE TIME BETWEEN RETRIES?

div.h1: BACKOFF RETRY VS. LINEAR RETRY STRATEGY
